Privacy Policy for Eitto

Effective Date: 14/03/2025

Thank you for playing Eitto. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains our practices regarding data collection, usage, and storage.

1. No Data Collection
Eitto is an offline game that does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data or user information. We do not track your activity, gather analytics, or request personal details.

2. No Internet Connectivity
Since Eitto is entirely offline, there is no internet communication during gameplay. This means no information is shared or uploaded to any server.

3. Third-Party Services
Eitto does not use any third-party services that may collect user data.

4. Children's Privacy
As we do not collect any data, Eitto is safe for all ages. We fully comply with privacy regulations such as the **Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA)** and **General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)**.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy if necessary. If changes are made, the updated version will be made available with a revised effective date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

eittogaming@gmail.com

By playing Eitto, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

